<DocsLayout title="API Reference" activeSection="api">
  <h1>API Reference</h1>

  <p>Base URL: <code>https://flick-server-production.up.railway.app/api/v1</code></p>

  <h2>Authentication</h2>

  <p>Two auth methods:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Session cookie</strong> &mdash; used by the dashboard UI. Set via <code>POST /auth/login</code>.</li>
    <li><strong>API key</strong> &mdash; used by SDKs and MCP server. Pass as <code>Authorization: Bearer flk_...</code></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Response Format</h2>

  <p>All responses follow the same envelope:</p>

  <pre><code>// Success (single)
{"{"} "data": {"{"} ... {"}"} {"}"}

// Success (list)
{"{"} "data": [...], "cursor": "...", "has_more": true {"}"}

// Error
{"{"} "error": {"{"} "code": "NOT_FOUND", "message": "Flag not found" {"}"} {"}"}</code></pre>

  <hr />

  <h2>Auth</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Method</th><th>Path</th><th>Auth</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>GET</code></td><td><code>/auth/config</code></td><td>None</td><td>Auth mode and SAML availability</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST</code></td><td><code>/auth/login</code></td><td>None</td><td>Email/password login, sets session cookie</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST</code></td><td><code>/auth/logout</code></td><td>None</td><td>Clear session cookie</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>GET</code></td><td><code>/auth/me</code></td><td>Session</td><td>Current user</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>GET</code></td><td><code>/auth/saml/login</code></td><td>None</td><td>Redirect to SAML IdP</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST</code></td><td><code>/auth/saml/callback</code></td><td>None</td><td>SAML assertion consumer service</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3>POST /auth/login</h3>

  <pre><code>{"{"} "email": "user@example.com", "password": "..." {"}"}</code></pre>

  <p>Returns user object and sets <code>session</code> cookie (httpOnly, 7 days).</p>
  <p>Rate limited: 5 attempts/min per IP, 10 attempts/5min per email.</p>

