  <h3>POST group</h3>

  <pre><code>{"{"}
  "name": "Pro Users",
  "slug": "pro-users",
  "rules": [
    {"{"} "attribute": "plan", "operator": "eq", "value": "pro" {"}"},
    {"{"} "attribute": "country", "operator": "in", "value": ["US", "CA"] {"}"}
  ]
{"}"}</code></pre>

  <p>Rules within a group are AND'd. Multiple groups on a flag are OR'd.</p>

