  <p>Webhook payloads are signed with HMAC-SHA256 via the <code>X-Flick-Signature</code> header.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>Rate Limits</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Endpoint</th><th>Limit</th><th>Window</th><th>Key</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>POST /auth/login</code></td><td>5 requests</td><td>60s</td><td>Per IP</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST /auth/login</code></td><td>10 requests</td><td>5min</td><td>Per email</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST /evaluate</code></td><td>1000 requests</td><td>10s</td><td>Per API key</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>POST /evaluate/batch</code></td><td>1000 requests</td><td>10s</td><td>Per API key</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>GET /evaluate/config</code></td><td>1000 requests</td><td>10s</td><td>Per API key</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>Rate limit headers on every response:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>X-RateLimit-Limit</code> &mdash; max requests in window</li>
    <li><code>X-RateLimit-Remaining</code> &mdash; remaining requests</li>
    <li><code>X-RateLimit-Reset</code> &mdash; Unix timestamp when window resets</li>
    <li><code>Retry-After</code> &mdash; seconds until retry (only on 429)</li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>Health Check</h2>

  <pre><code>GET /health → {"{"} "status": "ok" {"}"}</code></pre>
